{"tid":2449640,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JW王灝兒認加簽無綫經理人合約 　期待有劇拍：自己好鍾意演戲","createTime":"2021-03-17T00:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T02:54:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"64638e5adaabd7ac1dff52d57b123f9fdf18f77c","tid":2449640,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:00:39.000Z","msg":"王灝兒（JW）今晚（16/3）現身將軍澳電視城出席音樂節目《流行經典50年》錄影。已跟無綫加簽經理人合約的JW，直言可以歌視雙線發展：「其實我發現咗自己係好鍾意演戲，咁所以都希望嚟近都可以多啲拍劇，除咗拍劇之外，自己嘅歌都一路籌備緊。（拍劇要剪頭髮，怕唔怕影響做歌手形象？）咁又唔驚喎，因為而家啲假髮好勁，咁所以我覺得又唔使咁驚嘅。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210316/448604702456680448634971.jpeg/-bQ3W-k4dEboukQJ9mVf-tHhmhdKKad-k6Vst7mlbLc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210316%2F448604702456680448634971.jpeg%2F-bQ3W-k4dEboukQJ9mVf-tHhmhdKKad-k6Vst7mlbLc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=974fe30b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f2ac638b1b5eb3d9f8202c078528bcd6d63d70e","tid":2449640,"uid":55519,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:02:51.000Z","msg":"唔太想睇孝淵做戲"},{"pid":"7424b5f08a3784993eae41351e1a2942f51e9b2b","tid":2449640,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:05:24.000Z","msg":"搞咩要入TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aaf89928ec55500dbd9518b4c582d3d360079ab","tid":2449640,"uid":117037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:35:51.000Z","msg":"好想知佢同個肥仔點做愛"},{"pid":"7adafee11278105904fc48fc27b36ac63c00c1b1","tid":2449640,"uid":186189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aaf89928ec55500dbd9518b4c582d3d360079ab","tid":2449640,"uid":117037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:35:51.000Z","msg":"好想知佢同個肥仔點做愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"Jw由頭騎到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif